'''Nizeria''' to '''Nigeria''' kele nsi ya nene na [[Afelika]] ya Lumonso. Yandi kele na bantu ya kuluta bansi ya nkaka ya Afelika. Bansi ya pembeni kele [[Benin]], [[Tasadi]], [[Kamerun]] ye [[Nize]]. [[mbanza|Bambanza]] ya nene ya Nizeria kele [[Abuja]], [[Lagos]], [[Ibadan]], [[Enugu]], [[Kano]], [[Owere]], [[Sokoto]] ye [[Benin]].

== Bantu ==

*[[bahausa]] ná [[bafula]] 29 %
*[[bayoruba]] 21 %
*[[baigbo]] 18 %
*[[baidjo]] 10 %
*[[bakanuri]] 4 %
*bantu ya nkaka 18 %

== Bizunga ==

Nizeria kele na bizunga 36 ná ndambu mosi. Bizunga kele:  [[Abia]], [[Adamawa]], [[Kwa Ibo]], [[Anambra]], [[Bauchi]], [[Bayelsa]], [[Benwe]], [[Borno]], [[Cross River]], [[Delta]], [[Ebonyi]], [[Ẹdo]], [[Ekiti]], [[Enụgụ]], [[Gombe]], [[Imo]], [[Jigawa]], [[Kaduna]], [[Kano]], [[Katsina]], [[Kebbi]], [[Kogi]], [[Kuwara]], [[Lagos]], [[Nassarawa]], [[Niger]], [[Ogun]], [[Ondo]], [[Ọsun]], [[Ọyọ]], [[Plateau]], [[Rivers]], [[Sokoto]], [[Taraba]], [[Yobe]], [[Zamfara]] ye ndambu ya [[Abuja]].

